com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter

Interface IPeerApplicationManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IComponent, IHasAttributes, IPeerApplicationReader, IPeerApplicationWriter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PeerApplicationManager, PeerApplicationManagerService

    public interface IPeerApplicationManager
extends IPeerApplicationWriter, IPeerApplicationReader
    Peer application manager.

    Classes implementing this interface may be used as a single point of reference for a IPeerApplicationWriter and IPeerApplicationReader when they are to be shared by multiple components.

      • Fields inherited from interface com.camerontec.catalys.server.component.IComponent
